channel.title: It don't work
channel.description:
Hello,
I've downloaded Pimpscape, placed the files in the HybridScape folder and compiled it. Hybridscape works, but with pimpscape it sais:
NPC.cfg Not found Shops.cfg Not found Worlditems.cfg Not found etc.
I have JRE + JDK 5.0, 6.1, 6.3, 6.10 (it didn't worked first so i downloaded a few other versions) With other sources as Pimpscape it's the same error...
Why it gives errors? Can anyone fix it please? Thx
Bas
